			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a0683fdbcde443dca8ce8a18fa3471b2?s=68&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68 photo' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn">Philip</span> on <a href="http://wildtruth.net/#comment-1428"><time datetime="2014-06-21T11:10:10+00:00">June 21, 2014 at 11:10 am</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
