				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/8eb83c0cca0e9ac8732a943eebb0f184?s=68&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68 photo' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn">Chris</span> on <a href="http://wildtruth.net/#comment-1127"><time datetime="2014-04-09T19:00:55+00:00">April 9, 2014 at 7:00 pm</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
