			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/3fde027378ac945b9eebfd9024a264f7?s=68&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68 photo' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn">Ela</span> on <a href="http://wildtruth.net/#comment-473"><time datetime="2013-05-13T06:49:06+00:00">May 13, 2013 at 6:49 am</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
